text: Saint-Georges-d'Aunay is a former commune. It is found in the Normandy region in the Calvados department in the northwest of France. On 1 January 2016, it was merged into the new commune of Seulline.Arrêté préfectoral 17 December 2015 == References == Category:Former communes in Calvados
title: Saint-Georges-d'Aunay
